instruction: Make ASCII art of a cat
output:
Here's a simple ASCII art of a cat:

```
   /_/\
  ( o o )
   \_/
```

You can also use more complex characters to make the cat look more realistic. Here's an example:

```
   /_/\
  ( o o )
   \_/
  /   \
 /     \
|   |   |
|   |   |
|   |   |
 \   \  /
  \   \/
```

You can add more details like whiskers, eyes, and a tail to make the cat look more realistic. The possibilities are endless!
